Several people has come up with the opinion that Cristiano Ronaldo deserves the award more than the winner Lionel Messi. This was expected as this debate has been going on for years. English broadcaster Piers Morgan is also of the opinion and has took to his twitter page to express his discontent. See tweet below:   Messi international goals: 70. Ronaldo international goals: 99. There’s only one G.O.A.T.. and it’s this guy: @Cristiano⁩  pic.twitter.com/xOf57INpU8 — Piers Morgan (@piersmorgan) December 3, 2019 